text: Sampo () is a 1959 Soviet Finnish fantasy movie directed by Aleksandr Ptushko and Risto Orko.САМПОСампо It stars Andris Ošiņš, Eve Kivi, and Anna Orochko. ==Actors== * Andris Ošiņš as Lemminkäinen * Eve Kivi as Annikki * Anna Orochko as Louhi * Ivan Voronov as Ilmarinen * Urho Somersalmi as Väinämöinen == References == ==Other websites== * Category:1959 fantasy movies Category:Russian fantasy movies Category:Soviet fantasy movies Category:Finnish movies Category:Movies directed by Aleksandr Ptushko
